<i>noun</i>: 후덕 [후ː덕], 선행 [선ː행], 미덕 [미ː덕], 덕행 [더캥], 덕성 [덕썽], 덕목 [덩목], 덕 [덕] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>후덕 [후ː덕]</dt><br>
<dd>virtue; generosity; benevolence</dd><br>
<dd>말과 행동, 성품 등이 어질고 덕이 후함.</dd><br>
<dd>One's words, action, and personality being virtuous and generous.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>선행 [선ː행]</dt><br>
<dd>virtue; beneficence</dd><br>
<dd>착하고 올바른 행동.</dd><br>
<dd>A kind, good deed.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>미덕 [미ː덕]</dt><br>
<dd>virtue</dd><br>
<dd>칭찬을 받을 만큼 아름답고 훌륭한 태도나 행위.</dd><br>
<dd>An attitude or action which is good or respectable enough to merit praise.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>덕행 [더캥]</dt><br>
<dd>moral conduct; virtue</dd><br>
<dd>어질고 너그러운 행실.</dd><br>
<dd>A behavior that is gentle and generous.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>덕성 [덕썽]</dt><br>
<dd>virtue; moral nature</dd><br>
<dd>남을 넓게 이해하는 너그러운 성격.</dd><br>
<dd>The generous personality of someone who understands and accepts others.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>덕목 [덩목]</dt><br>
<dd>virtue</dd><br>
<dd>도덕적, 윤리적으로 실현해야 할 이상의 종류.</dd><br>
<dd>Kind of moral and ethical ideals to be realized.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>덕 [덕]</dt><br>
<dd>1. virtue</dd><br>
<dd>남을 이해하고 받아들이는 너그럽고 도덕적인 인격.</dd><br>
<dd>Generous and moral character capable of understanding and accepting others.</dd><br>
<dd>2. help; favor</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 사람이 베풀어 준 은혜나 도움.</dd><br>
<dd>Favor or help that someone else gives.</dd><br>
<dd>3. virtue; character</dd><br>
<dd>좋은 일을 하여 쌓은 업적과 훌륭한 인품.</dd><br>
<dd>The achievements accrued and the virtuous character built by doing good deeds.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>